.Dd June 24, 2026
.Dt X11DND_TARGET_GET_ACTION 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm x11dnd_target_get_action
.Nd retrieve the action Atom from a target session
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libx11dnd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In x11dnd.h
.Ft Atom
.Fn x11dnd_target_get_action "X11DndTargetSession *sess"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn x11dnd_target_get_action
returns the action
.Vt Atom
from the last
.Li XdndPosition
message received by the target,
or
.Dv None
if no position has been received.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
The action
.Vt Atom ,
or
.Dv None .
